reviewText: I own this on vhs & it is a must to go to dvd on this one. Most times I buy this type of product and am very upset when I see how I wasted my $. Not here! This is awesome+. Some of it is not that great,but the segments under the thatched roof are where you will use the repeat feature and the slow motion & stop action. That segment alone is worth the price.
